{"tid":1599341,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"報道指林鄭月娥尋求習近平批准正式撤回修例","createTime":"2019-09-28T02:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T03:50:25.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7473e5007925ab422e1dd5e0e858312e258630e3","tid":1599341,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:26:51.000Z","msg":"有報道引述特區政府消息指，行政長官林鄭月娥月初宣布將會正式撤回修訂逃犯條例前，尋求得到國家主席習近平批准。報道指撤回修例是重要決定，就像中央任命港府主要官員，因此必需得到習近平批准。<br />\n<br />\n北京認為修例風波不再是香港及中央的問題，而是涉及中美關係，港府在處理今次政治危機上沒有太大空間；另一名消息人士說，從國家安全角度，習近平批准撤回修例是自然及符合邏輯的做法，習近平在本月三號批准決定，林鄭月娥翌日發表電視講話，宣布政府將撤回修例，指北京表示理解，並尊重特區政府的決定。"},{"pid":"4c1883ce37d5a57a81ec8bffe97eb989e394d3da","tid":1599341,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:27:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1179131&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1179131%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOj9agwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=9eb27053\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1179131&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"10cfd91631d48c03317f528d2b9c2aa0da3ecf4b","tid":1599341,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T02:32:48.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqHqyQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqHqyQK.jpg&h=0796b3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線請留低你嘅DNA!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCHujkN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2